---
config:
  look: handDrawn
  theme: neutral
---
graph TD
    Start([make deploy-staging]) --> Parse[Phase 1: Parsing]

    Parse --> ParseOps[Read Makefile<br/>Expand variables<br/>Evaluate conditionals<br/>Build dependency graph]

    ParseOps --> ParseCheck{Parse<br/>Successful?}
    ParseCheck -->|No| ParseError[✗ Parsing Errors<br/>• Syntax errors<br/>• Undefined variables<br/>• Include failures<br/>• Malformed rules]

    ParseCheck -->|Yes| Resolve[Phase 2: Dependency Resolution]

    Resolve --> ResolveOps[Check file timestamps<br/>Identify phony targets<br/>Determine execution order<br/>Build target list]

    ResolveOps --> ResolveCheck{Dependencies<br/>Valid?}
    ResolveCheck -->|No| ResolveError[✗ Dependency Errors<br/>• Wrong execution order<br/>• Missing prerequisites<br/>• Circular dependencies<br/>• Phony target issues]

    ResolveCheck -->|Yes| Execute[Phase 3: Execution]

    Execute --> ExecOps[Run shell commands<br/>Execute recipes<br/>Update timestamps<br/>Check exit codes]

    ExecOps --> ExecCheck{Execution<br/>Successful?}
    ExecCheck -->|No| ExecError[✗ Execution Errors<br/>• Command failures<br/>• Environment issues<br/>• Resource problems<br/>• Permission errors]

    ExecCheck -->|Yes| Success([✓ Target Complete])

    ParseError --> End([Build Failed])
    ResolveError --> End
    ExecError --> End

    classDef whiteBox fill:#ffffff,stroke:#000000

    class Parse,ParseOps,Resolve,ResolveOps,Execute,ExecOps whiteBox
    class ParseCheck,ResolveCheck,ExecCheck whiteBox
    class ParseError,ResolveError,ExecError whiteBox
    class Start,Success,End whiteBox
